She commented on the outcome of the informal EU summit in Salzburg.
The Brexit decision was made in 2016 following a referendum.
The withdrawal of the United Kingdom is expected to take place by April 2019, but negotiations with Brussels on this issue are complicated by many factors.
In particular, there is still no clear agreement on how the parties will interact after London leaves the community.
The question of the Irish border remains open.
